## POSTMAN

    :my-environment = http://104.168.50.241:5000/api

### Get server info

    GET :my-environment/ 	

### Create an account

    POST :my-environment/accounts/
    Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8
    {
      "user": "Yohan",
      "description": "My budget",
      "currency": "EUR",
      "balance": 100
    }        

### Get all data for the specified account

    GET :my-environment/accounts/:user

### Remove specified account

    DELETE :my-environment/accounts/:user 	

### Add a transaction

    POST :my-environment/accounts/:user/transactions
    Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8
    {
      "date": "2020-07-23T18:25:43.511Z",
      "object": "Bought a book",
      "amount": -20
    }

### Remove specified transaction

    DELETE :my-environment/accounts/:user/transactions/:id
